title: Production of Rye in Canada 2016
summary: The graph shows the Production of Rye Canada ( in Tonnes ) in Canada the year 2016 .
Production is very different over the year .
While a significant decline in Production can be observed from January to February , Production continues to rise until April , reaching its annual maximum of more than 42000 Tonnes .
gold: The grapg shows the production of rye in canada in the year of 2016 . While production is very low during the winter months , more is produced during the summer months . In September , the annual maximum of almost 25000 tonnes is reached .
